  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a prospective pilot study to evaluate the usability and applicability of a self
      monitoring test of visual function with the handheld Health Management Tool (HMT) to remotely
      monitor neovascular Age Related Macular Degeneration (AMD) to detect a potential change in
      disease status.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
